    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Art movement lead by American painters Morgan Russell and Stanton Macdonald-Wright in the early 20th century. The style is distinguished for its focus on abstract, rhythmic color arrangements and submerged forms.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere al movimiento de arte dirigido por los pintores Americanos Morgan Russell y Stanton Macdonald-Wright a principios del siglo XX. El estilo se distingue por su enfoque abstracto y rítmico en la disposición del color, y formas inmergidas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Kunstbeweging uit het begin van de 20ste eeuw, met als leidende figuren de Amerikaanse schilders Morgan Russell en Stanton Macdonald-Wright. De stijl onderscheidt zich door een nadruk op een abstracte, ritmische kleurenrangschikking en vage vormen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052571/Jager, Stijlengids (1980)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>二十世紀早期，由美國畫家摩根‧拉塞爾（Morgan Russell）和斯坦頓‧麥克唐納‧賴特（Stanton Macdonald-Wright）為首的藝術運動。該風格的特殊性在於其聚焦於抽象、具節奏感的色彩配置，以及隱匿的形式。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
